":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1670319927","name":"windows","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1670319927","title":"Windows","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","topics":3478,"footer":"","header":"Windows, not walls.","title_alternative":"Windows","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1670319927","stars":1147,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":360,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"id":273463,"username":"Virace","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Virace","website":"https://x-item.com","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/142d/f888/273463_mini.png?m=1698848774","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/142d/f888/273463_normal.png?m=1698848774","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/142d/f888/273463_large.png?m=1698848774","created":1512824304,"last_modified":1698848774},"last_reply_by":"TomCN","last_touched":1699197162,"title":"从微软商店下载的程序，它们的开机启动项 数据存放在那？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/988841","created":1699186110,"deleted":0,"content":"像传统常用的就这两个键值来存放启动项\r\n```\r\nHKEY_CURRENT_USER\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Run\r\nHKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Run\r\n```\r\n\r\n但是从微软商店下载的程序数据就不存在这里，像火绒那个启动项管理就看不到。\r\n\r\n起因是 RoundedTB(任务栏圆角)和 TranslucentTB(任务栏透亚克力)，这两个软件冲突，系统会默认先启动 TranslucentTB 这样会导致，一些 bug 。如果先启动 RoundedTB 再启动 TranslucentTB 就没有这个问题了。\r\n\r\n想着说写个脚本呢来管理全部启动项，能单独延迟啊或者是等待某个进程启动后才启动某个程序。\r\n\r\n但是得先拿到管理启动项的方法，传统启动项可以操作上面两个键内的字符串。\r\n\r\n那么微软商店的程序，启动项存放在什么位置呢？\r\n另外，再任务管理器中禁止的启动项，这部分数据又存放在哪呢？","content_rendered":"<p>像传统常用的就这两个键值来存放启动项</p>\n<pre><code>HKEY_CURRENT_USER\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Run\nHKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Run\n</code></pre>\n<p>但是从微软商店下载的程序数据就不存在这里，像火绒那个启动项管理就看不到。</p>\n<p>起因是 RoundedTB(任务栏圆角)和 TranslucentTB(任务栏透亚克力)，这两个软件冲突，系统会默认先启动 TranslucentTB 这样会导致，一些 bug 。如果先启动 RoundedTB 再启动 TranslucentTB 就没有这个问题了。</p>\n<p>想着说写个脚本呢来管理全部启动项，能单独延迟啊或者是等待某个进程启动后才启动某个程序。</p>\n<p>但是得先拿到管理启动项的方法，传统启动项可以操作上面两个键内的字符串。</p>\n<p>那么微软商店的程序，启动项存放在什么位置呢？\n另外，再任务管理器中禁止的启动项，这部分数据又存放在哪呢？</p>\n","last_modified":1699186110,"replies":11,"id":988841},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_large.png?m=1680100270","name":"openai","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_normal.png?m=1680100270","title":"OpenAI","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/openai","topics":1532,"footer":"","header":"关于 OpenAI 旗下产品 GPT，DALL·E，和 ChatGPT 的讨论。请不要在 V2EX 的回复中粘贴复制来自 AI 生成的文本。","title_alternative":"OpenAI","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_mini.png?m=1680100270","stars":1802,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":1135,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"id":39068,"username":"haolly","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/haolly","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"广州","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7fbb/006d/39068_mini.png?m=1699181684","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7fbb/006d/39068_normal.png?m=1699181684","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7fbb/006d/39068_large.png?m=1699181684","created":1368621796,"last_modified":1699181684},"last_reply_by":"louzhichen","last_touched":1699194055,"title":"有没有国内可以用的 gpt 的 api ？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/988834","created":1699181753,"deleted":0,"content":"试了两个，一个 https://api.v3.cm/ 充值了 25 元，\r\n另一个 https://aikey.one/ 充值了 19.99 元，\r\n\r\n然后使用他们的 key 跟接口地址来使用，结果两个都提示类似的错误，感觉不靠谱。。。\r\n\r\n```\r\nHTTP code 200 from API (<!doctype html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charset=\"utf-8\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"logo.png\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"/><meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#ffffff\"/><meta name=\"description\" content=\"OpenAI 接口聚合管理，支持多种渠道包括 Azure ，可用于二次分发管理 key ，仅单可执行文件，已打包好 Docker 镜像，一键部署，开箱即用\"/><title>One API</title